    "body" : "<p>The name in jdbc will not have the table in it.</p>\n\n<p>You can either</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>work with positional parameters ( <code>getString (1);</code> and so on )</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>Or</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>define column name alias in your select (<code>select a.name namefroma from tableone a</code> )</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>Or</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>simply do rs.getString  (\"column\"); without the table prefix if name is unambigous</li>\n</ul>\n"
